Version 0.1-0 -- 2008-10-21

    o	First Release

    o   This 'RPostgreSQL' package was developed as a part of Google Summer of
     	Code 2008 program.

    o   Its implements all the features in the DBI (and a few extra like those
        related to transaction management)
